{"tid":447322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺搭扶手電梯 左行右企 好反智？","createTime":"2017-10-25T07:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T08:43:40.000Z","uid":143269,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"822e9e47d4c514ea6a95682e0cf0209649f3d002","tid":447322,"uid":143269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"原本呢種norm係方便急既人係左邊行，快d去到第二層<br />\n但繁忙時間搭mtr果陣成日見到d人其實唔想行、想企右邊，但右邊不斷有人行，咁佢就停係lift口 等位攝入去，搞到後面塞曬，反而耗咗更多時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/153904_b659c02439eaa1a87127c54be945e3ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F153904_b659c02439eaa1a87127c54be945e3ea.jpg&h=74ba24c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時有d人明明唔想行，但唔小心企咗左邊，成條左手邊都無人果陣，因為群眾壓力/從眾心理 被逼行翻上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/154203_26cc1e9769051c10ab65f614f021669c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F154203_26cc1e9769051c10ab65f614f021669c.jpg&h=dea162be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\ni）令唔想行既人被逼行上去<br />\nii）單行搭 +塞住後面，令人搭lift用多咗時間"},{"pid":"01db2197848355b6ddf5ba6891342e6d677d43ef","tid":447322,"uid":36815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"覺"},{"pid":"2553d9a00144c3c22e44edbe3de5049f7a60f408","tid":447322,"uid":141435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"噉可以點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8996f8a66a1fbc0b99327a51e4656df4cf3094","tid":447322,"uid":79370,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"我認為兩行一齊行最好"},{"pid":"62b0456919a2de74e30d35075bd6f6a6b8295ff2","tid":447322,"uid":75998,"like":1,