:133205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"叫啲仆街同廢老玩少陣電話咪可以快啲囉"},{"pid":"2c33613e540bf8d04f4bd48e020315d4eebfb2bb","tid":447322,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間不嬲企左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗鐵職員都叫人企晒兩邊"},{"pid":"a311ec4219ad3080fca71a5b1fda33bb5d958b5d","tid":447322,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"其實兩邊都應該企先安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}